          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Under this assumption, the total cross section in the",
                "region investigated is expected to follow the",
                "approximate relation given below. sigmat = alpha",
                "sqrt(Er/E)*(1+2E/Er) + sigmas, sigmat = total cross",
                "section, E = neutron energy, Er = resonance energy =",
                "4.8 eV. The scattering cross section sigmas, is",
                "assumed to be approximately constant, while alpha is",
                "a constant depending on the Breit-Wigner parameters",
                "of the 4.8-eV resonance as is given below. alpha =",
                "sigma0 Gamma**2 /4*Er**2, sigma0 = cross section at",
                "resonance, and Gamma = resonance width."
              ]
            }
          ],
